social_posts.post_text:
Moriah has pulled out four molars this week. The last (I think) of her baby teeth. Or I guess those are premolars. 

They have been rolling around on my bed trying to say which one of them is gonna win the super secret spy game they are playing. I told them they are pretty awful spies since I now know all the secrets. 

#siblings #lazyday

I am ever thankful that the Botox and steroids this month have kept the migraines at bay. I’ve been more than a week without one! Almost two weeks. 

However the steroids haven’t helped the itchy hives at all and that’s what they were actually for.

This cat put himself under the covers and laid on the pillow like a human. He crawled up the covers from the bottom and just laid like that. He’s so ridiculous. And when I walked out of the room he mewled at me like he was telling me to turn the lights out lol. I did though and he’s laying up there asleep. 

#orangecat #orangetabby

.

social_posts.post_text: And that doesn’t count my Apple Books or the thousands of fanfics I’ve read this year.

Come by and see me! I’ll be at Ragtime Cafe until 6pm. 

And tomorrow I’ll be at Rio’s in Helena from 6-7pm. 

#liquorsampling #brandambassador #bulleit

Woke up with a migraine today. I guess it’s the weather. I just got all the kids out the door and I was finally laying back down when I hear one of the cats loudly singing the call of it’s people. She was ‘stuck’ in the bathroom. And by stuck I mean the door was open two inches but she is lazy. 

Also Moriah is adorable. She wants to do makeup everyday now. It’s a pain getting her to leave the mirror to get on the bus.

I am very excited to announce that I joined the amazing people at Encompass Health Rehabilitation this week. I started orientation on Monday and training yesterday. It is a part time position with full benefits and a great pay. I already love the people I’m going to be working with. 

Moriah is not happy with this transition. She wants me to be here every day when she gets off the bus. 

Also I have to wear long sleeves every day and dress business casual so I have to buy some new clothes.
I’m gonna be at Margarita Grill in Pelham tonight giving out shots of 21 Seeds Tequila! Come see me! I’ve got swag to give out as well.

Alexander Ovechcat says hello and what’s for breakfast? He gave me a vigorous hand washing when I interrupted his bath so I am just going to take his picture and stop interrupting him. 

.
#tuxedocat #alexanderovechcat #ovi #omgwafc #morningswithmycat

Come see me at the St. Lucky's St. Patrick's Day Crawl - Birmingham - 6th Annual! It starts at Carrigan's Beer Garden (Lakeview)

#crawlwithus #barcrawl

I need a new moisturizer for daytime. I’ve been using Cerave with sunscreen but it’s flaky. It peels off my skin? 

I think I need something thicker but definitely have to have the sunscreen. On the medicines I’m on apparently it makes me allergic to the sun even indirect sun. 

any suggestions?

I am not proud of how long and loud I laughed at this. I guess they don’t call me the queen of dorks for nothing. 

#dadjokes #humor #memes

Saw this on a friends FB. I love possums. My dad calls them all Fred. 

#possummemes #screamqueens

Moriah wakes up screaming. I’m like it’s ok baby, it’s ok! 

Moriah: I had a bad dream. It was so scary. We went to the beach and there was a giant monster!

Me: that does sound scary 

Moriah: oh the monster wasn’t scary, he just lived there at the beach

Me: ummm then why was it a bad dream

Moriah: Taylor tried to push me in an ant bed even though she knows I’m scared of ants

Now she’s napping on and off because she got ‘bad sleep’ according to her. Ignore my laundry in the background. I’ll do it one day. 
.
. #thisiswhatautismlookslike #youngestchild #baddreams #motherhood

It’s my baby’s 21st birthday! Can you believe I brought this little demon in the world 21 years ago? 

7:03 pm 4/28/02.  8lbs, 8oz 21.5 inches 

Matthew was the best thing that ever happened to me. He has been my one constant. It was just us for a long time when I was a single mom and I’m glad Eric has been a great dad to him since then. 

#firstchild #teenmom #oldestchild #sundayschild

‘I’m not bad, I’m just drawn that way’ - Jessica Rabbit 

Cats are lovely little demons and I appreciate both their cuddles and their apathy. 

#cats #imnotbadimjustdrawnthatway #catsareawesome

Be you! Be free. Don’t let anyone take that from you. Drink water, take your meds, and give your pets a cuddle. 

And speaking as someone who has been called queen of the dorks since she was 8, things get better. Life goes on. And being weird has brought me so much joy in my 30’s. 

#weirdkids #beauthentic #beweird #queenofthedorks

Moriah painted this for me at a birthday party. Shout out to Lydia for her love of opossums! 

She says it’s me and she even added my nose ring and painted nails. 

#opossums #kidart #ahhhhhh

We had a music class performance this afternoon and now we have a strings performance tonight for the whole school system. Lots of music today I guess lol. Moriah plays the viola so she’s been excited.
Let me sleep! Insomnia is my evil nemesis but at least we can make some funny jokes about it.

New glasses for my my little bat. She has degenerative myopia so these are her third pair in a year. The eye doctor says it seems to be slowing down though! Thank you to atropine drops at night. 

They are a forest green with a lighter green on the inside. I am so happy that GlassesUSA.com had the color she wanted.
Addie Kristen Ford I feel like this frog is you for some reason

It’s May. This is ridiculous. Come on Alabama weather. RealFeel 107° is just gross. 

#WeatherInTheSouth

Last day of 6th grade for this demon. He actually skipped the last couple of days since his testing was done last Thursday. 

Elijah is 5’8 now and really enjoys the Magnus Chase series and Factoria. 

#lastdayofschool #juniorhigh

And last day of 4th grade for Moriah. She did her makeup and she had a hat on earlier that’s she’s since lost lol. She told me that she just didn’t have enough glitter on her face for her last day. 

She still loves Funneh & the Krew on YouTube, reading graphic novels, and making up stories/songs. She has hit a growth spurt and I’ve had to buy clothes several times over the school year. She went from 8/10 to 14/16 and all her pants are too short too. 

#lastdayofschool #4thgrade #thisiswhatautismlookslike
It’s me!!!!
Like in Percy Jackson when there was a casino where time stood still. Las Vegas always seems kind of magical in a tarnished money kind of way.

I’m usually smiling at work but yesterday I got told my smile was an innocent smile. Hmm. 

#workselfies #redhead #ginger

"Proud and insolent youth,” said Hook, “prepare to meet thy doom.” 

“Dark and sinister man,” Peter answered, “have at thee."

We did four days of staycation this week. It was lovely. I didn’t take a lot of pics to be in the moment but the kids said they had fun. I go back to work tomorrow. 

We played at three different libraries, we swam, we played in the rain, we ate a lot of food, we watched movies, we washed our cars. Moriah wanted the air dryer until it turned on and then she cried because it was loud. 

And to round out a nice vacation Eric took us to a steakhouse for a fancy lunch. The kids really loved that. Elijah was mad I wouldn’t let him order a 20oz porterhouse lol.
Well Courtney Oldham I guess I found your alt account

My favorite meme

One of my fav quotes. I think it’s a good day for a Neruda quote except I feel it’s too early. 

I love you as 
certain dark things are to be loved,
In secret, 
Between the shadow and the soul 

-Neruda
Right?

Moriah’s binder from last year. She wants to use it again. She says it’s ‘bedazzled’ but it’s already falling apart. 

I have no idea where I got all those stickers lol. Maybe her bday? She says she won’t take another binder that doesn’t have her fav stickers on it.
null

Starting my Virta journey. I am prediabetic and with my Hashimotos I need to make some lifestyle changes. My insurance recommended #Virta to me and I just got my supplies. I’ve got the recipe book open now to start meal planning for the week. 

Wish me luck! 
.
.
.
.
#hashimotos #prediabetes #weightloss

Here is my cool kid. She’s wearing a @bhambarons jersey shirt with a @nhlblackhawks Stanley Cup Championship hat. She said if someone came up and said her teams suck she would tell them they were gross. 

#coolkid #blackhawks #birminghambarons #thisiswhatautismlookslike
Still one of my favorite quotes and a good book as well.
Just say no to sparkling water

My very favorite gift from my wedding is broken :( I am so sad! @shuncutlery has been a part of my kitchen for so long and this was my favorite paring knife. I have no idea how this even happened but I’m sad. 

#kitchenmishaps #shuncutlery #shun #paringknife

My very favorite gift from my wedding is broken 😞 I am so sad! Shun Cutlery-KAI USA Ltd. has been a part of my kitchen for so long and this was my favorite paring knife. I have no idea how this even happened but I’m sad. 

#kitchenmishaps #shuncutlery #shun #paringknife

It’s daughters day! Moriah is my sunshine. She’s never met a stranger and will jump into any conversation. She is a slightly shyer version of Mat Eubank honestly. She’s very body conscious lately and says she hates herself so we make sure to tell her how lovely and sweet she is often.
My kids put my cast iron skillet in the dishwasher again! My poor baby 😞

Old friends and new friends. We are having a Halloween movie party with Catherine Valladares grand girls and Moriah. 

So we are stuffed with good food and the girls are painting pumpkins while we watch Hocus Pocus.
Skittle cotton candy pizza #halloweentreats #kidparty

My kids and their best friend at Trunk or Treat. The 13 year old decided to be Oppenheimer (no he has not watched the movie). He picked his clothes from the thrift store. He even pretended to cough because Oppenheimer had TB. 

The 10 year old decided to be a emo depressed teenager. She even wore a dirty giant hoodie and too big pants. She walked around going ‘this isn’t a phase bruh’ 

And the 11 year old was Ghost from Modern Warfare 2019. He let me know there was a distinction in years and he pieced together his costume over the past 6 months. 

At least we have creative kids.
Eric Balog turned 38 yesterday but I worked till 8. So I made steak and salmon for him today when I got off at 6. Matthew even came over to celebrate his dad.

The Halloween Bar Crawl - Birmingham (Fri & Sat) - 6th Annual is tonight as well. 

Come see me! I’ve got swag and it’s gonna be fun! 7 different locations for the Crawl and free Jell-O shots with tickets. 

I’m about to put my costume on. Putting all this stuff together is hot work.
Somehow Eric didn’t see a bunch of Warriorettes put candy all over our yard and a sign. He’s in the living room watching tv. Glad to know he would definitely hear a killer coming

This is the only photo they would let me take. They had a good time though trick or treating. We visited Matthew at work. Then we came home and I made brown rice to go with roast. Moriah did get overwhelmed though by so many flashing lights and kids running around. She’s sleeping in our room tonight. 

Halloween 2023 is now finished. It really doesn’t even feel like October yet and now tomorrow its November.
Nikita Gill is so lovely. Some of the best quotes.

Eric and that jacket. Hes gonna wear it until it literally falls apart. 

Two of the boys I love. My husband and my cat. They are both grumpy butts.

Well Ovi is at the vet and Eric says it’s gonna be $445. They are sedating him and lancing the spot. They may have to put a drain in. And it’s so expensive. 

My sweet baby. #alexanderovechcat #ovi #hurtpet

Moriah wanted a new style for Christmas. And Elijah got a trim because he says his style is already amazing. 

#ChristmasHair #newyearnewme
Merry Christmas Eve to everyone who celebrates! I am at work today but happy to home by 6 pm to see my babies. Eric has been sick the last few days so I hope he’ll be better soon.
She’s giving us a Christmas concert with her viola. She plucked a few songs and then used used her bow.

You know those people that say they hate animals and then they come over and all the animals bother them? It’s my husband. He complains about the cats endlessly and yet he always has one of them. He even types across the cats every day while he works. 

#pets #cats #gingercat #earlthecat

This is why I have a Pacific Rim tattoo. Being drift compatible is beautiful to me. Something larger than being a best friend or lover or family. Being able to share parts of your very being with someone.
